data.description: Discover the epitome of lakeside living in this exquisite Logan Martin lakefront home. Boasting main-level living, this gorgeous residence offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. Step inside to find a spacious rec room with a full bath in the basement, ideal for entertaining guests or creating a cozy retreat. The expansive decks, featuring open, covered, and screened areas, provide unparalleled views of the tranquil waters! For water enthusiasts, this property is a dream come true. Enjoy the convenience of a private boat dock, constructed just 2 yrs ago, with a depth of 7 feet for easy access to the lake. The electric boatlift adds a touch of convenience. Nestled on a mostly flat lot, this home offers unobstructed BIG water views that will take your breath away. The outdoor kitchen is perfect for hosting barbecues and gatherings, while the stone firepit adds a touch of warmth and ambiance for cozy evenings by the lake. Come experience the ultimate lakefront living today!
